@CompositionGateway_HostAddress = https://localhost:7126
@orderId = 08bebbee-0e7e-4368-afab-74f4720f5f4e
@customerId = 01093176-1308-493a-8f67-da5d278e2375
@productId = 9ea20ee6-d6bd-4654-80fb-3dd7e52792f9
@creditCardId = be09bff7-ab1c-499d-9e40-a282de05cd88
@deliveryOptionId = 17779198-9ae4-419c-8373-65aa4c050cf7

### Browse: default product list
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/products
Accept: application/json

### Browse: filtered list. Categories/Breweries/Countries/Sort/Page/Size are query-string parameters, not path segments
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/products?categories=Beer&page=1&size=12
Accept: application/json

### Browse: facet sidebar data
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/products/facets
Accept: application/json

### Browse: single product
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/product/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

### Cart: read cart contents
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/cart/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### Cart: add a product (quantity is a +/- delta against the existing line)
POST {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/cart/addproduct/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Cart: "Proceed to checkout" submit. Body is a raw JSON array of cart lines that replaces the cart slice
POST {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/cart/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "productId": "{{productId}}", "quantity": 1 }
]

### Checkout - address: read billing + shipping address screen
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/address/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### Checkout - address: submit. Body must carry BOTH envelopes because Finance reads `billingAddress` and Shipping reads `shippingAddress` from the same POST
POST {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/address/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "billingAddress": {
    "fullName": "Dennis van der Stelt",
    "street": "Van Zandvlietplein 1",
    "zipCode": "3077 AA",
    "town": "Rotterdam",
    "country": "The Netherlands"
  },
  "shippingAddress": {
    "fullName": "Dennis van der Stelt",
    "street": "Van Zandvlietplein 1",
    "zipCode": "3077 AA",
    "town": "Rotterdam",
    "country": "The Netherlands"
  }
}

### Checkout - shipping: read delivery options + cart
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/shipping/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### Checkout - shipping: pick a delivery option. Shipping and Finance both read this same body
POST {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/shipping/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryOptionId": "{{deliveryOptionId}}"
}

### Checkout - payment: list the customer's saved cards
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/creditcard/{{customerId}}
Accept: application/json

### Checkout - payment: read payment screen
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/payment/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### Checkout - payment: pick a stored card
POST {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/payment/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "creditCardId": "{{creditCardId}}"
}

### Checkout - summary: final review screen
GET {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/summary/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### Checkout - submit: triggers the atomic checkout dispatch. No body
POST {{CompositionGateway_HostAddress}}/buy/summary/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
